# 🎮 Hangman Game (Python)

A simple command-line **Hangman Game** built using Python.
In this game, the player guesses letters to reveal a hidden word before running out of lives.

---

## 📌 Features

* 🎲 Random word selection
* 📝 Input validation
* 🔁 Prevents duplicate guesses
* ❤️ 6 lives system
* 🎨 ASCII Hangman graphics
* 🏆 Win/Lose detection
* 📋 Displays guessed letters
* 📈 Shows current word progress after every guess

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Python 3
* `random` module

## 💡 Concepts Used

* Variables
* Lists
* Loops
* Conditional Statements
* Functions (can be added later)
* String Manipulation
* Input Validation
* Random Module
* Game Logic
* ASCII Art

